{'title': 'Stocks Tracker Widget (open-source)', 'description': "Stocks Widget is a home screen widget that displays stock price quotes from your portfolio\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n‚òÖ Completely resizable, it will fit the number columns base on the width you set.\r\n‚òÖ Scrollable, so you don't have to worry about adding more widgets\r\n‚òÖ Stocks are sorted by change in percent (descending), or you can rearrange them yourself\r\n‚òÖ You can set custom refresh intervals and start/end times\r\n‚òÖ You can import and export your portfolio from a textfile\r\n‚òÖ Add multiple portfolios to multiple widgets\r\n‚òÖ View recent news for your tracked symbols\r\n‚òÖ View graphs for your tracked symbols\r\n‚òÖ Open sourced here https://github.com/premnirmal/StockTicker", 'descriptionHTML': 'Stocks Widget is a home screen widget that displays stock price quotes from your portfolio<br><br>Features:<br>‚òÖ Completely resizable, it will fit the number columns base on the width you set.<br>‚òÖ Scrollable, so you don&#39;t have to worry about adding more widgets<br>‚òÖ Stocks are sorted by change in percent (descending), or you can rearrange them yourself<br>‚òÖ You can set custom refresh intervals and start/end times<br>‚òÖ You can import and export your portfolio from a textfile<br>‚òÖ Add multiple portfolios to multiple widgets<br>‚òÖ View recent news for your tracked symbols<br>‚òÖ View graphs for your tracked symbols<br>‚òÖ Open sourced here https://github.com/premnirmal/StockTicker', 'summary': 'A home screen widget that displays stock price quotes from your portfolio', 'summaryHTML': 'A home screen widget that displays stock price quotes from your portfolio', 'installs': '100,000+', 'minInstalls': 100000, 'score': 4.605, 'ratings': 2019, 'reviews': 748, 'histogram': [50, 30, 121, 262, 1554], 'price': 0, 'free': True, 'currency': 'USD', 'sale': False, 'saleTime': None, 'originalPrice': None, 'saleText': None, 'offersIAP': None, 'size': '5.0M', 'androidVersion': '4.0.3', 'androidV